@startuml
title Scene JSON の守備範囲図

top to bottom direction
skinparam backgroundColor white
skinparam shadowing true
skinparam dpi 150
skinparam defaultFontName Yu Gothic UI
skinparam defaultFontSize 18
skinparam rectangle {
  RoundCorner 24
  BorderColor black
  BackgroundColor #f7fbff
  FontColor black
}
skinparam ArrowColor black
skinparam ranksep 20
skinparam nodesep 20

rectangle "camera" as Camera
rectangle "HUD / guide /\nstatus" as Hud
rectangle "input\nactions" as InputActions
rectangle "Scene JSON" as SceneJson #e0f0ff
rectangle "primitive\nentries" as PrimitiveEntries
rectangle "model\nentries" as ModelEntries
rectangle "tileMap" as TileMap
rectangle "animation /\nmetadata" as Metadata
rectangle "ModelAsset" as ModelAsset #fff8ef

Camera --> SceneJson
Hud --> SceneJson
InputActions --> SceneJson

SceneJson --> PrimitiveEntries
SceneJson --> ModelEntries
SceneJson --> TileMap
SceneJson -right-> Metadata
Metadata .right.> ModelAsset : 参照

'Camera -[hidden]down-> Hud
'Hud -[hidden]down-> InputActions
'PrimitiveEntries -[hidden]down-> ModelEntries
'ModelEntries -[hidden]down-> TileMap
'TileMap -[hidden]down-> Metadata
'Metadata -[hidden]down-> ModelAsset
'InputActions -[hidden]right-> SceneJson
'SceneJson -[hidden]right-> PrimitiveEntries

note left of SceneJson
1 モデルではなくシーン全体の
初期状態を宣言する
end note

@enduml
